Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.39,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.47,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:37.55,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.11,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:15.25,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:22.60,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:27.33,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:34.27,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:01:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saint-Juste-sama, who was taken from us all too soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she were still here with us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure that she would be laughing with joy. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm writing to tell you about something new and wonderful that has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It happened on the final day of the week-long Port Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Held each year to celebrate summer's end, it is the largest religious festival in these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That day was the first time that I have gone with both my mother and my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Papa, look! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There, over by the second stone lantern.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce you. This is Orihara Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She will be coming with me to Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Takehiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,39. A Lingering Fragrance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, we're done with that horrid assignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, making us write a report on our impressions of Hemingway's works in English!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't do that to us, can they?! Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we managed somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we managed. I couldn't have done it without your help, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It was no trouble, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is the right area, but where's this new place of Mariko's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that there's supposed to be a kids' playground nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's a pretty nice-looking place, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is really small compared to our old house, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama and I share a bedroom, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the veranda... look at this, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's okay, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A castle for just the two of us, for Mama and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Mama! Bring out some of that Darjeeling tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, and some of the {\i1}creme brulee{\i0} cake, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tea and cake are our only luxuries now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you can hear the steam whistles from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I don't know whether that's a good thing or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I heard that Papa said that he'd like to see me each month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to think on it a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, when it comes down to it, Papa was the one who betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My Papa had a son whom he didn't see for thirteen years...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that son decided to get married...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa saw then that his son had truly grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa didn't say a word to us then, but he looked so very happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But still... you know what I thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As happy as Papa looked to be at the time, I'm sure that he was still feeling the sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and pain over all the time together that they never had.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I've just been a bit out of it recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'll never see Saint-Juste-sama again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just felt kind of strange ever since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been concerning myself with other people's issues and ignoring my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,None of that, now. I think the girl {\i1}still{\i0} hasn't gotten her emotions sorted out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No... no, I don't think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that Nanako-san has simply grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem so much more mature than us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the same age, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not going to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never going to understand other people's feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking of others just doesn't sit well with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really aren't going to go see your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I'd {\i1}think{\i0} about it, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What, like you're really the model of maturity yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, me? Heck, I could even be a mother by now, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What's with you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, like I said, don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just be concentrating on getting ready for your studies in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the reception hall, just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know some people and we can get something set up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, have you made the arrangements for her for while you're over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctors, a school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You called for me, Takashi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm sorry to trouble you, but could you prepare dinner a bit early tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some things that I need to get back to work on this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The preparations for the wedding ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, among other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly are a good friend to Henmi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's heading off to Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show him a good time while he's still here in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have found someone truly wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even better than Fukiko-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Igarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry sir, that was very rude of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then... I shall start the dinner preparations at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko... where is she right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She left a while ago to go riding at the club, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In one summer, in one week...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the love of a lifetime was forged...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rei... Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the end, you never did fall in love with a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If... if you had found someone to love...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...what would your love have been like, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike me, you were truly free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You would be willing to devote yourself to someone, to give in to all your passions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You would give your very life for it, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Painful though it may be, love is a truly wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really did want to see you fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to see you even more radiant than ever before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I only regret that I never saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shall I compare thee to a summer's day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thou art more lovely and more temperate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fukiko-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fukiko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that your love?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that all that there is to your love?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One summer, one week, and then nothing more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That wasn't love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my one love in this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are like I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have not yet known true love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A toast to you, may you find love anew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A new love? Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That was it, that was the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My one and only love...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall never love another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I swore, upon my very life...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was getting so late, I was worried that you might have fallen or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you thinking about Rei again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No, that wasn't it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rei... is this what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The new semester is finally here, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been through some pretty difficult ordeals this summer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...you've managed to sort out your feelings over it all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And how about physically?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Everything's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then... what's on your mind? You were the one who invited me out this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The new semester is starting, and you invited me out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,as though you wanted to ask me something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So... what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but be a bit anxious,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,wondering what sort of question you'll spring on me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh goodness, Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to ask you something when you're already jumping ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something you feel nervous about asking, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I really {\i1}am{\i0} getting nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Whatever it is, I'll give you a straight answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to ask you, Papa. I wanted to ask you first, before asking Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For a while now... for quite a while, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your real daughter, Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know about my real father. I want to know everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you love me, Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to understand how important that is to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:14:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I think that we could still be just as happy even if we never discussed this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I would hate to think that something truly important to me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,might one day be lost forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Papa! Tell me anything that you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is my father? Where is he now? What kind of person is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Mama never did marry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, she did live with him for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...but once you were conceived, and before you were born, she left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I know... No, it is all speculation, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never once asked your Mam about any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand why, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I were to ask her, she is not the sort of person who would ever want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For my sake, or for yours... perhaps for both of us, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...I think that Mama has chosen to keep those things locked away forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I love her dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She is beautiful in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with that, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For your Papa here, things are fine as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am who I am; you are your own person, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If the time comes someday when you feel that you truly must know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...then don't hesitate on my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and ask Mama if she will unlock those secrets within her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But... that's why I came to you, Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because even you know that Mama is not the sort who would ever tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you, Nanako, must have one or two secrets that you will keep locked away forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even knowing that, you can still love and believe in someone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well anyway... we're going to be late for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so began the new term.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mariko-san's suspension was reduced, too, so she was able to start the new semester with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Misaki-san, Sonobe-san, Furuta-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...all of those who had been Sorority members before it was abolished...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and of course, Miya-sama as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those bright summer days were coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So many things had happend; but it was over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each of us had overcome something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You could see it in our faces... cheerful, confident, perhaps a bit more mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only one person was with us no more. Like the wind, she bade us farewell, and left forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She will forever shine brightly in our hearts, one page in the story of our youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, the seasons changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I watched Kaoru-no-Kimi's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the final match of the area league championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the final game for Seiran Academy's ace, Kaoru-no-Kimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaoru-no-Kimi wore the number "16" in that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That number once belonged to her, to Saint-Juste-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No doubt, Kaoru-no-Kimi fought that final match with that person at her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clearly the other students from Seiran Academy noticed it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone was applauding and cheering just as loudly as they could as they watched the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then came the most important day of all, for both you and Kaoru-no-Kimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was raining that day, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi Takehiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...do you promise to love this woman, Orihara Kaoru, as your wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...through times of sickness, through times of health, for all time, until death do you part?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Orihara Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...do you promise to love this man, Henmi Takehiko, as your husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...through times of sickness, through times of health, for all time, until death do you part?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For so long as I shall live...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that eighteen-year-old bride shone more brightly that day than anything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her lips, painted a delicate rose, and her cheeks, touched with blush...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was truly full of life that day, living for the sake of love, shining for all to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"For so long as I shall live..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those words filled her heart as she spoke them for the one she loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someday, I, too, will be able to say such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what I was thinking that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will one day be able to say such words as those.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope to someday find such a love, that I can say such words as those...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish it with all my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wonderful, isn't it, Kaoru-no-Kimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All the romantic country roads, and then there's the Rhine river...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, and the sausage there is supposed to be really good, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get the chance, we're going to tour some of the old castles, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid... just splendid...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... splendid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Be happy, Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I mean it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Henmi. It's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Be well... Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Takehiko-san. You take care, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Kaoru-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:21:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For just a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For just a moment, as I stood there beside my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I caught the nostalgic scent of that one person who will never again return.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That scent, Saint-Juste-sama's fragrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That subtle, masculine air...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps it was the scent of tobacco that so often surrounded her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The plane carried away not only my brother and Kaoru-no-Kimi,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but also that nostalgic lingering fragrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since then, the cherry blossoms have bloomed twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a senior at Seiran Academy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.88,0:23:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just received the wonderful news from Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother, I have something wonderful to tell you, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recently, I have met someone whom I've taken a bit of a liking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a second-year student at the University...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...although... he doesn't have dark-brown eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.66,0:24:13.86,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.86,0:24:19.33,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:24.94,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.94,0:24:30.41,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:36.69,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.69,0:24:42.16,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.16,0:24:44.89,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.89,0:24:47.70,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.70,0:24:50.10,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.10,0:24:55.37,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
